Cosmos University: Deities Databank

This Databank contains entries on three hundred and eighty-four deities and their associations to their respective pantheons, spiritual properties, and ritualistic practices. This information is currently being gathered and updated as we accumulate it.

If you're interested in helping: We are always on the lookout for incorrect information within this databank, often times deity names aren't correctly described in source materials and as a result we create duplicate entries on accident. We are still gathering good source materials for the role of deities in spiritual practices. Additionally we're facing a large backlog of historical data (lineages, properties, and stories) that we would invite help in processing.
